<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; }
        .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; background: #fafafa; }
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; color: #fff; background: #000; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 40px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:24px;">CALVORO</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
            <p>Hey <%= username %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password. If you didn't do this, you can just ignore this email.</p>
            <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
            <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px; color: #999;">This link will expire in 1 hour.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Calvoro. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
